{"TopicId":151293,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Combat Mission: Black Sea","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-01T21:06:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-01T21:06:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone here play any of the Combat Mission games? I just got into them, so I\u0027d like to hear your experiences about them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-01T22:46:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoa, looks like a 3D Close Combat or somesuch. Had no idea these existed, I might check them out (loved CC3).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-02T00:34:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222833880\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478040372\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270807\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022regex\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, regex said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoa, looks like a 3D Close Combat or somesuch. Had no idea these existed, I might check them out (loved CC3).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey have a free demo. I\u0027m playing it right now. It\u0027s super realistic, but you have to micromanage a ton of stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-02T03:42:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222834053\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478046899\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey have a free demo. I\u0027m playing it right now. It\u0027s super realistic, but you have to micromanage a ton of stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImplying real combat has no micromanaging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022where\u0027d that rail lock for my carry handle go?\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u0022batteries? Oops, forgot those, now my sight is useless\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u0022oh, forgot my MRE heater bag, guess I\u0027m not eating!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-02T03:47:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222834279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478058165\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImplying real combat has no micromanaging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNormally a Captain or Major doesn\u0027t have to tell a Sergent how to breach into a building.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Captain tells a platoon to lead left, and the other to head to the center. He doesn\u0027t have to say \u0022take cover behind this building.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nCM puts you in command of a reinforced company, ususally, but it also wants you to do the thinking for your Lt.s and Sergents.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-02T03:57:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222834282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478058445\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNormally a Captain or Major doesn\u0027t have to tell a Sergent how to breach into a building.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Captain tells a platoon to lead left, and the other to head to the center. He doesn\u0027t have to say \u0022take cover behind this building.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nCM puts you in command of a reinforced company, ususally, but it also wants you to do the thinking for your Lt.s and Sergents.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, that\u0027s lots of micromanaging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nARMA is more realistic in that aspect of your sergeants/platoon leaders/etc being competent.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-02T05:17:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222834282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478058445\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNormally a Captain or Major doesn\u0027t have to tell a Sergent how to breach into a building.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Captain tells a platoon to lead left, and the other to head to the center. He doesn\u0027t have to say \u0022take cover behind this building.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the higher gets the officer\u0027s rank, the simpler are rules and game pieces, the flatter is the game board...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-02T05:19:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222834380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478063825\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the higher gets the officer\u0027s rank, the simpler are rules and game pieces, the flatter is the game board...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo paraphrase Patton, commanders should order units one link down the chain and know the positions of units two down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-02T05:23:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, and\u00A0 sergeant plays Counterstrike, Leutenant plays with soldiers, Captain with cars and cannons, Colonel with tokens, General with arrows, high-rank General throws a coin...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-03T21:40:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222834386\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478064182\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/1/2016 at 10:23 PM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsergeant plays Counterstrike\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, if they\u0027re in Russia the Counter Strike would help.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}